Nollywood actor Lateef Adedimeji has said that he is a man of many incredible virtues while indulging fans to affirm his assertion. ‘Crying Machine’ as he is also called stated he is someone who doesn’t shy away from his flaws even as he continuously works to become a better version of himself. The 35-year-old movie star, however, appealed to his fans to be patient with him in the process of achieving perfection. Taking to his Instgram, the actor wrote: “There’s a lot of beauty in me, can you see it? I own up to my weaknesses as I try to become a better man, but in the process of achieving perfection, will you be patient with me? It is what it is…”